---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Privacy Policy — Chitti" description="Learn how Chitti protects your privacy and handles your data with care.">

  <section class="py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-text">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-text-light">Last updated: 6 April 2026</p>

      <div class="prose-policy mt-12 space-y-10">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            Welcome to Chitti ("App," "Platform," or "Service"). This Privacy Policy explains in detail how Chitti ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, shares, stores, protects, and manages your personal data, including facial information. By using the Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">2. Data Collection</h2>

          <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-text">2.1 Face Data</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            Chitti collects photos you submit via the app's camera or photo library. These photos may contain facial imagery including skin tone, skin texture, and facial structure for beauty and skincare analysis.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We do not extract, compute, or store facial geometry, faceprints, biometric templates, or any form of biometric identifier. No facial recognition technology is used at any point.
          </p>

          <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-text">2.2 Other Personal Information</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We also collect the following personal information:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-text-light">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Name</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Age</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Gender</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Phone number</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Coarse location (city or region)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Product collection (skincare and beauty products you use)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Conversation history (text-based chat interactions with AI specialists, including AI-generated analysis results but not the photos themselves)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Preferences (tone preference, persona selection, and context choices)</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">3. Usage of Face Data</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            The collected facial data is exclusively used for the following purposes:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-text-light">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Analysing skin condition, skin tone, hair characteristics, and makeup application</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Generating personalised beauty and skincare recommendations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Providing visual feedback on your style and appearance (Vibe Check)</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            Face data is never used for facial recognition, identification of individuals, surveillance, profiling, advertising, or training any AI model.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">4. Third-Party Sharing & Storage</h2>

          <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-text">4.1 Third-Party Providers and Why We Share Data</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            When you use an analysis feature (Vibe Check, Skin Analysis, or Makeup Analysis), your photo (which may contain facial imagery) and any accompanying text context you provide are sent to <strong class="text-text">OpenAI</strong> for the sole purpose of generating your personalised analysis and recommendations.
          </p>

          <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-text">4.2 Third-Party Storage Practices</h3>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-text-light">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Cloud infrastructure providers:</strong> Used for secure, encrypted storage of account data, conversation history, and photos (where applicable). They do not independently access or analyse your data.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">OpenAI:</strong> Processes your photo and text in real-time to generate analysis. OpenAI does not retain, store, or log your photos or personal information after the analysis response is generated. Your data is never used by OpenAI to train, fine-tune, or improve any AI model or service. OpenAI is contractually prohibited from sharing your data with any other party. All data submitted through our Service falls under OpenAI's zero-data-retention API policy.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Google Analytics:</strong> Used for understanding aggregated usage patterns. No photos, face data, or personally identifiable information is shared for analytics purposes.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to any third party for marketing or advertising purposes.
          </p>

          <h3 class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold text-text">4.3 Data Storage Locations</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            All collected data, including photos and related metadata, is securely stored in cloud infrastructure compliant with industry-standard data protection practices and security standards.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-text-light">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Vibe Check photos:</strong> Not stored. Processed in real-time and discarded after the analysis response.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Skin Analysis photos:</strong> Not stored. Processed in real-time and discarded after the analysis response.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Makeup Analysis photos:</strong> Stored securely for up to 7 days to support the analysis workflow, then automatically and permanently deleted.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Account data and preferences:</strong> Retained for as long as your account is active.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Conversation history:</strong> Retained for the duration of your account so you can access past recommendations.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We do not retain face data indefinitely without a specific, stated purpose. When you delete your account, all personally identifiable data is permanently deleted within 30 days.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">6. User Consent & Transparency</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            Before your first analysis, the app displays a consent screen that clearly explains your photo will be sent to OpenAI for analysis. You must tap "I Agree" to proceed. If you decline, analysis features will not be available, but you can still use all other features of the app.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            Consent may be withdrawn at any time by ceasing to use the analysis features or by requesting account deletion through the app's settings.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">7. User Rights (DPDP/GDPR Compliance)</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            Under applicable laws and standards (DPDP Act, GDPR, and global privacy regulations), you hold the following rights regarding your data:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-text-light">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Right to Access:</strong> You can access your personal information within the app at any time.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Right to Correction:</strong> You can update your profile information within the app.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Right to Data Portability:</strong> You may request a copy of your personal data by contacting us.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Right to Erasure:</strong> You can permanently delete your account from within the app by navigating to Settings and selecting "Delete Account." All personal data — account information, conversation history, product data, preferences, and any stored photos — is permanently deleted within 30 days. This action is irreversible.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:chitti.connect@gmail.com" class="font-medium text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 hover:decoration-primary">chitti.connect@gmail.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">8. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We maintain stringent security protocols to protect your data:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-text-light">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>All data is encrypted in transit (TLS 1.3) and at rest (AES-256).</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Database access is enforced through row-level security policies, ensuring your data is accessible only to your authenticated account.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Photos are accessed via short-lived, signed URLs that expire within minutes.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Photos, face data, and personally identifiable content are never written to application logs or analytics systems.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            Chitti is designed for users aged 13 and above. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware that a user younger than 13 has provided us with personal information, we will take immediate steps to permanently delete that information.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">10. Cookies and Third-Party Analytics</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We utilise cookies and employ third-party analytics tools for app functionality optimisation and aggregated user engagement analytics. Our analytics provider is Google. No photos, face data, or personally identifiable information is shared for analytics purposes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">11. Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            For privacy concerns, queries, or grievances, please contact us at <a href="mailto:chitti.connect@gmail.com" class="font-medium text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 hover:decoration-primary">chitti.connect@gmail.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">12. Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            This Privacy Policy may be periodically updated to comply with evolving legal requirements or changes in our data handling practices. Users will be notified via app notifications of significant policy changes. Continued use of the Service following these updates constitutes acceptance of the revised Privacy Policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Specific Disclosures Regarding Face Data (Addressing App Store Guideline 5.1.1)</h2>

          <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-text">What face data does the app collect?</p>
              <p class="mt-1 leading-relaxed text-text-light">Photos you submit for analysis, which may contain facial imagery such as skin tone, skin texture, and facial structure. No biometric identifiers, faceprints, or facial geometry are extracted.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-text">Why do we collect face data?</p>
              <p class="mt-1 leading-relaxed text-text-light">To analyse your skin condition, hair characteristics, and makeup application in order to provide personalised beauty and skincare recommendations.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-text">Is face data shared with third parties?</p>
              <p class="mt-1 leading-relaxed text-text-light">Yes. Your photo is sent to OpenAI for AI-powered analysis. OpenAI processes it in real-time and does not retain it after the response is generated. OpenAI does not use your data for model training or share it with any other party.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-text">Is face data used for tracking or advertising?</p>
              <p class="mt-1 leading-relaxed text-text-light">No. Face data is used solely for the beauty analysis you requested.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-text">Is face data used to train AI models?</p>
              <p class="mt-1 leading-relaxed text-text-light">No. Our contract with OpenAI explicitly prohibits the use of your data for model training, improvement, or any purpose other than generating your requested analysis.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-text">How long is face data stored and why?</p>
              <p class="mt-1 leading-relaxed text-text-light">Vibe Check and Skin Analysis photos are not stored — they are processed in real-time and discarded. Makeup Analysis photos are stored encrypted for up to 7 days to support the analysis workflow, then permanently deleted. OpenAI retains nothing beyond each individual request.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-text">Do third parties store face data?</p>
              <p class="mt-1 leading-relaxed text-text-light">Cloud infrastructure providers store encrypted photos (for Makeup Analysis only) but do not access or analyse them. OpenAI does not store or retain any face data.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-text">How does the user consent to data sharing?</p>
              <p class="mt-1 leading-relaxed text-text-light">The app displays a consent screen before the first analysis, clearly explaining that photos will be sent to OpenAI for analysis. The user must agree to proceed.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-medium text-text">Can the user delete their data?</p>
              <p class="mt-1 leading-relaxed text-text-light">Yes. Users can delete their account from the app's Settings. All personal data is permanently removed within 30 days.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</PageLayout>
